{
  "2244970": {
    "name": "No More Snow",
    "steam_appid": 2244970,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >一路战斗通过 16 个独特的关卡！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244970/extras/052249b9ccc2878a82674d74186b5695.poster.avif?t=1764522470\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244970/extras/052249b9ccc2878a82674d74186b5695.webm?t=1764522470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244970/extras/052249b9ccc2878a82674d74186b5695.mp4?t=1764522470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一路杀出一条血路，穿过高山、森林小路、深洞、墓地、幽灵小镇，甚至圣诞老人的玩具工厂。体验总共 16 个关卡，全部以圣诞节和万圣节为主题。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >种类繁多的武器 - 找到你最喜欢的！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244970/extras/2f3988b82b1aa18ace6bf804cf75a163.poster.avif?t=1764522470\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244970/extras/2f3988b82b1aa18ace6bf804cf75a163.webm?t=1764522470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244970/extras/2f3988b82b1aa18ace6bf804cf75a163.mp4?t=1764522470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >礼品盒中有多种枪支和近战武器供您选择。从突击步枪和霰弹枪等轻型武器到迷你枪、火箭发射器和火焰喷射器等重型武器，每个人都能找到适合自己的东西。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >悠闲的单人或合作行动</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244970/extras/1be504b5715bfb70c6bfbd2b436381e7.poster.avif?t=1764522470\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244970/extras/1be504b5715bfb70c6bfbd2b436381e7.webm?t=1764522470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244970/extras/1be504b5715bfb70c6bfbd2b436381e7.mp4?t=1764522470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一起玩总是更有趣！在沙发上放松，拿起控制器，与朋友组队对抗坎普斯的爪牙。虽然游戏完全可以在单人模式下玩，但有一个同伴会让事情变得更容易，甚至更有趣。该游戏支持本地沙发合作和 Steam 远程同乐，但不提供在线多人游戏模式。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >大量的敌人和老板</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244970/extras/8094e294c58dcb2e2144cf9cddb31a54.poster.avif?t=1764522470\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244970/extras/8094e294c58dcb2e2144cf9cddb31a54.webm?t=1764522470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244970/extras/8094e294c58dcb2e2144cf9cddb31a54.mp4?t=1764522470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个关卡都会引入新的敌人类型，并以独特的 Boss 战告终。遇到他们，发现他们的弱点，并将他们打倒！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >季节性更新</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244970/extras/9f6b5ddf346bb17e2a20b73c2b21b0b9.poster.avif?t=1764522470\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244970/extras/9f6b5ddf346bb17e2a20b73c2b21b0b9.webm?t=1764522470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244970/extras/9f6b5ddf346bb17e2a20b73c2b21b0b9.mp4?t=1764522470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >圣诞节可能已经结束，但圣诞老人和坎普斯之间的战斗仍在继续！享受夏季和万圣节季节的免费内容更新，还有更多令人兴奋的新增内容。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >在 Steam Deck 上测试</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244970/extras/75dafa2a63ff437ca03cc98626179df8.poster.avif?t=1764522470\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244970/extras/75dafa2a63ff437ca03cc98626179df8.webm?t=1764522470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244970/extras/75dafa2a63ff437ca03cc98626179df8.mp4?t=1764522470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >该游戏在手持设备上完美运行！有什么比在旅途中轻松打发时间更好的呢？</p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语<strong>*</strong>, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 简体中文, 乌克兰语, 日语, 法语, 意大利语, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 西班牙语 - 拉丁美洲, 波兰语, 土耳其语<br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
